  clueName: Second talk with Lou
  description: "Lou has mark on her palm which she claims it came from a basketball
    injury. Though, it looks more like a burn mark. She says all she did was exchange
    glances with Mei, and quickly mention\u2019s Archie\u2019s presence near her
    when she was at the lockers before the meeting. She thinks that Archie was going
    to go confess his love for Mei."
